divs: Sighting Detailsaround 9:30 p.m. I saw flashing lights in the sky, which looked like a star. As I watched though it was pulsating and moving slowly. over the course of an hour it went in a completely different location and I could see rays coming off of it. It was very high up and during the same time, I did see planes in the sky, and it did not have the same characteristics. Also there were stars visible and they were not the same as this thing that I saw. A while later it was completely gone.
Summary: strange lights and movement in the sky
